headline: Strength Seen in Rockwell Automation (ROK): Can Its 10.7% Jump Turn into More Strength?
summary: Rockwell Automation (ROK) saw its shares surge in the last session with trading volume being higher than average. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions may not translate into further price increase in the near term.
